Package org.javact.compiler

Class Summary
ActorProfile Manipulating actor profiles.
AsynchronousMessage Class that implements the Message class and provides the handling of asynchronous messages.
BehaviorProfile Manipulating behavior profiles.
Driver An instance of this class manages the processing of files and the automatic generation of message handling classes.
Keywords This class contains the definition of JavAct terms external to the compiler and needed by it.
Main Main class.
Message Provides methods for processing the generation of message handling java files.
Options Class that defines the compiler options.
Signature This class provides tools for manipulating a message signature.
SynchronousMessage Class that implements the Message class and provides the handling of synchronous messages.
Tools Class that provides some tools not directly related to the JavAct application.
 

Exception Summary
ActorProfileException Exception that occurs when an ActorProfile interface both inherits behavior profiles and declares methods.
BecomeException This exception occurs when a BehaviorProfile interface declares malformed become methods (bad return type, bad number & type of parameters.
NotABehaviorProfileException Exception that occurs when a badly defined BehaviorProfile interface is parsed.
